 a market share of nearly 20%. With so many phones flying off shelves year after year, you may be wondering: where is the iPhone made, and how does the latest model reach customers so quickly each generation? Let’s break it down.\u003c/p\u003e\n"},{"resource":"nc-string","html":"\u003ch2\u003eBefore assembly: Where do iPhone components come from?\u003c/h2\u003e"},{"badges":[],"resource":"nc-img","image":{"src":"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-scaled.jpg","srcSet":"https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-scaled.jpg 1920w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-300w-170h.jpg 300w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-1200w-675h.jpg 1200w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-768w-432h.jpg 768w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-1536w-864h.jpg 1536w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-2048w-1152h.jpg 2048w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-16w-9h.jpg 16w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-32w-18h.jpg 32w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-28w-16h.jpg 28w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-56w-32h.jpg 56w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-64w-36h.jpg 64w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-712w-400h.jpg 712w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view-ifixit-1000w-563h.jpg 1000w, https://www.androidauthority.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/iphone-exploded-view